00045 void DataSetTest_GenericData::ColsFromDataSetWithZeroRows()
00046 {
00047         GenericData gd;
00048         GenericFileReader reader;
00049         reader.SetFilename("../data/small_cel_file_with_dataset_of_zero_rows");
00050         reader.ReadHeader(gd);
00051 
00052         // Open a DataSet that has 0 rows.
00053         DataSet* ds = gd.DataSet(0,3);
00054         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ds);
00055         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ds->Cols() == 2);
00056         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ds->Rows() == 0);
00057 
00058         ds->Delete();
00059 
00060         // Open another DataSet that has 0 rows.
00061         ds = gd.DataSet(0,4);
00062         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ds);
00063         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ds->Cols() == 2);
00064         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ds->Rows() == 0);
00065 
00066         ds->Delete();
00067 }
